            , joiner, now in court, being a<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177507120030"></xptr> relation of his own by his mother's side; and he is also well acquainted with 
               <persName id="t17750712-49-person397">
                  James
                   Lewis
               <interp inst="t17750712-49-person397" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750712-49-person397" type="given" value="James"></interp>
